Package us.conxio.HL7.HL7Stream

Interface Summary
HL7MessageHandler A interface for HL7Message dispatch handlers.
HL7Stream An abstract class to serve as a base for HL7 message stream classes.
 

Class Summary

HL7FileWriter Writes HL7Message objects to a file.
HL7Server A thread pooled HL7 Server.
HL7SocketStream A tcp socket stream object for reading and writing HL7Message objects.
HL7StreamBase A base class of default behaviors for HL7Stream objects.
HL7StreamURI A URI class for parsing HL7 i/o stream URIs.
 

Exception Summary
HL7IOException An exception class for HL7 message streams.
